{"tid":342073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【順天邨色魔】與疑犯同層    羅小姐︰好恐怖","createTime":"2017-07-31T10:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T16:29:41.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1436714500e890753952b399948b6938e5890f5","tid":342073,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170731/large/1501494990_77ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170731%2Flarge%2F1501494990_77ab.jpg&h=cb54ca2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順天邨企圖強姦案17歲疑犯今晨在寶達邨達怡樓吊頸身亡，街坊今日得悉事件均感驚訝，不少人議論紛紛。與疑犯住同層的羅小姐表示，今早由新聞得知涉嫌風化案的疑犯上吊亡，對疑犯原來一直與自己同層感到「好恐怖」，她上午外出時已見大批警員及警犬在其樓層調查。<br />\n<br />\n羅小姐稱，附近一帶的治安稍算良好，她平日都會出夜街，但日後會提高警覺。"},{"pid":"0b2dce09c16582d210cf01a0b192231c3ea2ef2d","tid":342073,"uid":40763,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:15:03.000Z","msg":"真係唔係冇血性<br />\n但係是但搵戶公屋既都住左十年八年<br />\n你都安然無恙<br />\n人地一面之緣就險被奸<br />\n係咪你個樣令人心寒d呢"},{"pid":"99b74c469848c079fcd611819848fa09a0f25640","tid":342073,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"btw 好耐都冇講呢句<br />\n關鳩你事咩飛影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10c0e04384f51b85801d39f9cdf6109b9082596","tid":342073,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"494bb06627772412877e87867021ea9ebcff4bce","tid":342073,"uid":29627,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"同一層咁耐都冇事發生<br />\n證明你好安全"},{"pid":"a5847e7216e5382ec50bf2b46de930f2fc765b49","tid":342073,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,